direction: right

*.style.border-radius: 8
*.style.font-size: 13
*.style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
*.style.stroke: "#333333"

# --- Entry ---

entry: |md
  **rfe-feasibility-review**
  internal sub-agent

  - Receives RFE ID
  - model: opus
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Read RFE ---

read-rfe: |md
  **Read RFE**

  - artifacts/rfe-tasks/{ID}.md
  - {ID}-comments.md (if exists)
  - Stakeholder context
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Architecture context ---

arch-context: |md
  **Architecture Context**

  - .context/architecture-context/
  - PLATFORM.md + components
  - Skip if unavailable
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

# --- Prior review ---

prior-review: |md
  **Prior Review**

  - rfe-review-report.md
  - What was addressed?
  - What remains?
  - New issues from revisions?
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Assess ---

assess: |md
  **Feasibility Assessment**
  LLM (opus)

  - Technically feasible?
  - Architectural conflicts?
  - Strategy alignment?
  - Scope realistic?
  - Hidden complexities?
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#e8e8e8"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
  style.double-border: true
}

# --- Output ---

write-output: |md
  **Write Assessment**

  - rfe-reviews/{ID}-feasibility.md
  - Verdict: feasible /
    infeasible / indeterminate
  - Strategy considerations
  - Blockers + scope assessment
| {
  shape: rectangle
  style.fill: "#f5f5f5"
  style.stroke: "#333333"
  style.stroke-width: 2
}

# --- Edges ---

entry -> read-rfe

read-rfe -> arch-context: {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

read-rfe -> prior-review: "if re-review"

prior-review -> assess

arch-context -> assess: {
  style.stroke-dash: 3
}

assess -> write-output
